GIMS Compliance Relay — Interactive Demo
Source-Available, Non-Production License
Copyright (c) 2026 BMA / GIMS. All rights reserved.

This repository contains a NON-FUNCTIONAL DEMONSTRATION of the GIMS Compliance
Relay user interface. It has no real backend, no real authentication, no real
cryptographic integrity, and no data persistence. It exists solely to show the
look, feel, and workflow of the product.

